@startuml LND_Studio_Pipeline_Flows
title Pipeline Flows — EC, MA, RP

skinparam {
  ActivityBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
  ActivityBorderColor #333333
  ArrowColor #555555
  defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
  defaultFontSize 11
  TitleFontSize 14
  PartitionBackgroundColor #F5F5F5
}

|EC Pipeline|
start
:User provides image + mood_seed;
:🖼️ **Kana** — Forensic Analysis
  ----
  OCR, character anchoring,
  explicit elements, heat map,
  gut reaction, fetish vector;
note right
  Output: forensic inline data
  Pass: fetish_tags, gut_reaction,
  explicit_acts, archetype
end note
:🌍 **Luna** — Scene Prelude
  ----
  Setting blueprint,
  relationship topology,
  "The Why", escalation arc,
  sensory anchors;
note right
  Output: prelude inline data
  Pass: setting_seed,
  power_dynamic, kink_name,
  sensory_anchors
end note
:🖋️ **Suki** — Caption Writer
  ----
  150-300 word Vietnamese prose
  Mandatory COT think block
  3 sensory anchors woven in;
:Write caption.json;
stop

|MA Pipeline|
start
:Raw Manga Page(s);
:🖼️ **Kana** — Panel Forensic
  → forensic-state.json;
:🖼️ **Kana** — POC Context Vectors;
:👤 **Aria** — Character Builder
  → character-bible.json;
:🖋️ **Suki** — R18 Prose Generation
  → draft-prose.json;
:🛡️ **Riko** — Quality Audit (100-pt)
  → audit-report.json;
if (Score ≥ 85?) then (PASS)
  :Final Output;
  stop
else (FAIL)
  if (3rd consecutive fail?) then (yes)
    :⚠️ HALT PIPELINE\nCircuit Breaker;
    stop
  else (no)
    :Rewrite loop → Suki;
  endif
endif

|RP Pipeline|
start
:User Turn (action/dialogue);
:🎭 **Yua** — Turn Planning
  ----
  <think> block:
  Turn deconstruct, archetype,
  sensory mirror, escalation,
  character pulse, principle check;
:🎭 **Yua** — Novel Format Output
  ----
  Narrator block (italic prose)
  + Character dialogue 「brackets」
  + Thoughts （parens）
  + SFX ***bold-italic***;
:Deliver turn;
stop

@enduml
